author: Shibani Mahtani
title: U.S. Says Myanmar Vote Key to Further Support
text:
YANGON—A senior U.S. official said Tuesday that Myanmar’s coming elections will be a crucial marker in determining whether relations between the two countries should be fully normalized, including lifting sanctions that still remain.
